{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/fingertips/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"dd4d09a3-d1bf-5c5f-9786-adbae103964a","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/662ce0a0c02105d6b1618efd829548a8/18e3b/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/662ce0a0c02105d6b1618efd829548a8/18e3b/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/662ce0a0c02105d6b1618efd829548a8/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/662ce0a0c02105d6b1618efd829548a8/18e3b/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Fingertips (aka Dashboard) is the main app that hosts all the other apps I built while working at Vodafone. Its purpose is to serve as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>the platform to access all the other available apps</li>\n<li>inform the users about news and updates</li>\n<li>have quick summaries about the apps using Widgets</li>\n<li>give feedback and have real-time support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Initially, there was just a page with boxes for the apps, but I thought we could rebuild it into something that has more information and would allow us to connect with our users. That’s how I came out with the dashboard and widgets design.</p>\n<p>After making a few mockups and sharing my ideas with the rest of the team, the project was approved and I started building it. I owned 100% of the front-end work, including the UX user testing sessions with Vodafone employees and some parts of the final design.</p>\n<p><strong>All the widgets and app tiles are draggable</strong>, so each user could organise the dashboard in whichever way they prefer. Widgets can also be added or removed, although there are some that are mandatory, like <code class=\"language-text\">news</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">feedback</code>.</p>\n<p>At the top of the app there is an horizontal scrolling slider that contains all the available apps. Some of them might be <code class=\"language-text\">locked</code>, so the user needs to access request by clicking on them. These requests are then managed from another section of the app.</p>\n<p>I also built widgets for various Vodafone RSS news feeds and for specific apps like Lighthouse, Bonsai or Boomerang. These app widgets show favourite items or a summary of the latest changes in those apps.</p>\n<p>Some of the widgets include pagination and others include settings.</p>\n<p>News stories and ideas have their own canonical URL and page. Ideas include comments from users as well.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a44f24c20eb7e8572b900fb4c789a6e/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.199999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"Add a new widget\"\n        src=\"/static/4a44f24c20eb7e8572b900fb4c789a6e/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a44f24c20eb7e8572b900fb4c789a6e/d1f95/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/4a44f24c20eb7e8572b900fb4c789a6e/dbdff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Add a new widget</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d9f79f92e3273adfde5b466a2964d952/dbdff/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"Idea page\"\n        src=\"/static/d9f79f92e3273adfde5b466a2964d952/dbdff/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d9f79f92e3273adfde5b466a2964d952/d1f95/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/d9f79f92e3273adfde5b466a2964d952/dbdff/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Idea page</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: 